<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. لا يُلْهِيَنَّكَ مَنْزِلٌ لَعِبْتَ بِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَيْدِي الْبِلا مِنْ سَالِفِ الأَزْمَانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَلَقَدْ تَرَحَّلَ عَنْهُ كُلُّ مُسَرَّةٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَتَبَدَلَتْ بَالْهَمِّ وَالأَحْزَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>سِجْنٌ يَضِيقُ بِصَاحِبِ الإِيمَانِ لَـ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>ـكِنْ جَنَّةُ الْمَأْوَى لِذِي الْكُفْرَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>سُكَّانُهَا أَهْلُ الْجَهَالَةِ وَالْبَطَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>لَةِ وَالسَّفَاهَةِ أَنْجَسُ السُّكَّانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَأَلَذُّهُمْ عَيْشًا فَأَجْهَلُهُمْ بِحَـ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>ـقِ اللهِ ثُمَّ حَقَائِقِ الْقُرْآنِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>عَمْرتْ بِهِمْ هَذِي الدِّيَارُ وَأَقْفَرَتْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مِنْهُمْ رُبُوعُ الْعِلْمِ وَالإِيمَانِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>قَدْ آثَرُوا الدُّنْيَا وَلَذَّةُ عَيْشِهَا الْـ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَانِي عَلَى الْجَنَّاتِ وَالرِّضْوَانِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>صَحِبُوا الأَمَانِي وَابْتُلُوا بِحُظُوظِهِمْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَرَضُوا بِكُلِّ مَذَلَّةٍ وَهَوَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>كَدْحًا وَكَدًا لا يُفَتَّرُ عَنْهُمْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>مَا فِيهِ مِنْ غَمٍّ وَمِنْ أَحْزَانِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَاللهِ لَوْ شَاهَدتَ هَاتَيْكَ الصُّدُو<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>رِ رَأَيْتَهَا كَمَرَاجِلِ النِّيرَانِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>